Author: wheresmywinegums
Text: I used to binge on candy hard. I can relate to that cut-up mouth feeling. I haven’t been able to eat sour keys in ages due to that, which is a minor win.   The major loss is that previously I “didn’t care that much about chocolate...” now, fuck me up with that chocolatey goodness. Doesn’t matter what kind, just all of it. Peanut butter too.

Author: FridgethatRidge
Text: Oof same. I just burned off 1,000 cals today, but I fucked it up and binged. It's okay though, you can always start over tomorrow.
